 <id type="desktop">virtaal.desktop</id>
 <licence>CC-BY-SA</licence>
 <description>
  <_p>
    Virtaal is a program for doing translation. It aims for a delightful combination of simplicity and power. It integrates with selected online resources to make translation fun, while helping to improve translation quality.
  </_p>
  <_p>
    The initial focus is on software translation (localization or l10n), but is definitely meant to be useful as a general purpose tool for Computer Aided Translation (CAT).
  </_p>
  <_p>
  </_p>
  <_p>Some features:</_p>
  <ul>
   <_li>Translation reuse (translation memory)</_li>
   <_li>Terminology assistance</_li>
   <_li>AutoCompletor and AutoCorrector</_li>
   <_li>Quality checks with customization for many languages</_li>
  </ul>
 </description>
